Package: forrel
Type: Package
Title: Relatedness Inference and Forensic Pedigree Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2018-20-07
Authors@R: person("Magnus Dehli", "Vigeland", email = "m.d.vigeland@medisin.uio.no", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Forensic applications of pedigree analysis, including marker simulation,
    relatedness inference and exclusion probailities. Data import from the Familias
    software is fully supported.
